HEADWORD: Homocategoric
<hw>Ho`mo*cat`e*gor"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Homo-</ets> + <ets>categoric</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Biol.)</fld>
<def>Belonging to the same category of individuality; -- a morphological
term applied to organisms so related.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Homocentric</ent>⟦br⟧
